attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Enjoy the best of South Boston with this spectacular 3-bed/3-bath penthouse duplex in an unbeatable location! Spanning 1,501 sqft across 2 levels, this spacious home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, & functionality. The open-concept layout is ideal for modern living, and storage is plentiful, with thoughtfully designed closets + additional storage areas throughout the home. Each bedroom is generously sized, while the meticulously renovated primary bathroom with gorgeous marble tile adds a luxurious touch to the primary suite. A beautifully designed roof deck with Southern exposure and gas fire pit is perfect for entertaining / relaxing. Central AC, hardwood floors, & deeded basement storage round out this property! Enjoy local favorites Petula's, Annie's, Sidewalk Cafe, The Paramount, Playwright, plus Starbucks, Stop & Shop, Walgreens, MyStryde/workout classes, shops, Medal of Honor Park, M St beach, Castle Island, Curley Center, and public transportation (buses & BlueBikes)!
